Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.00,0:00:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Onode—
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.38,0:00:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Raku!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.05,0:00:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, where are we supposed to take these journals?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.80,0:00:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Damn it! Right as I was about to talk to Onodera!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.18,0:00:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't the teacher just tell us to take it to the prep room?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.60,0:00:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, right! Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.31,0:00:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, by the way, Chitoge!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.69,0:00:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the science prep room, got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.53,0:00:52.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't go to the music room by mistake again!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.82,0:00:54.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Roger that!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.57,0:00:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Jeez.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.49,0:00:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Her first name?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.70,0:01:01.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.33,0:01:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, the other day we figured we should start calling each other by our first names.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.00,0:01:09.25,Default,,0,0,0,,One of her friends mentioned to her how odd it was that we weren't on a first-name basis,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.25,0:01:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,despite how long we've been dating.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.92,0:01:12.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Still not used to it, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.22,0:01:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Damn it, I hate having to flaunt my relationship in front of Onodera!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.39,0:01:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What a dilemma!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.35,0:01:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoot... She beat you to it, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.85,0:01:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,That hurt, Ruri-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.85,0:01:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you just start calling him by his first name, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.73,0:01:32.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I could never do that!
