Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.24,0:01:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Ichijou Raku! Have you seen Mistress?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.75,0:01:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, she was on her way to the science prep room.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.83,0:01:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. Well, that's convenient.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.46,0:01:57.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The truth is, there's something I wanted to talk about, but without letting her know.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.63,0:01:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Without letting her know?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.72,0:02:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Since everybody seems to be present, could you all spare a moment, please?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.47,0:02:03.85,Default,,0,0,0,,But Shuu's not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.85,0:02:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody seems to be present.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.43,0:02:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.35,0:02:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, today is Mistress's birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.19,0:02:15.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Thus, so that she may enjoy her special day,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.53,0:02:18.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm currently planning a surprise party for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.36,0:02:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I would very much like to invite you to the party.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.12,0:02:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,If you were to attend, I'm sure that Mistress would be overjoyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.70,0:02:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Really? Of course we'll go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.08,0:02:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That means we'll have to get her presents and stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.50,0:02:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I suppose if you absolutely insist,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.63,0:02:39.97,Default,,0,0,0,,being that you are Mistress's boyfriend and all...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.97,0:02:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I might be inclined to invite you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.76,0:02:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, not that I'd even want to see your ugly mug.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.26,0:02:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell? If I'm that revolting to you, then I won't bother!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.94,0:02:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,It would be awkward, anyway, being the only guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.52,0:02:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,No, come!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.40,0:02:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Make up your mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.73,0:02:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.53,0:02:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,After school, you two go buy her a present together!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.53,0:03:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,R-Ruri-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.07,0:03:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Miyamoto, why aren't you coming?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.20,0:03:07.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, sorry. Actually, I've had a stomachache all day.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.50,0:03:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! You had two Lunch Special A's today!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.08,0:03:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, you'll be able to pick out a gift faster if you bounce ideas off each other!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.21,0:03:15.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-Then Miyamoto, you should—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.59,0:03:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget about me, just go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.34,0:03:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, you two meet up by the cafe at five!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.59,0:03:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,And show up in your normal clothes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.89,0:03:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You're making us {\i1}change{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.10,0:03:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though you're not coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.61,0:03:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm so nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.65,0:03:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Man, I can't believe how bossy Miyamoto always manages to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.45,0:03:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can never figure out what's going through her mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.50,0:03:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I mean, meeting up with a girl here of all places?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.96,0:03:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That makes it look like we're on a date!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.38,0:03:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wait, this is a date? Is it a date?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.55,0:04:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If this is a date, then—putting aside that fake date—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.97,0:04:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}that would mean that my first date ever would be with Onodera!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.55,0:04:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No way! Picking out a present together, you can't call that a real date, can you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.68,0:04:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Damn it, I have no clue!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.27,0:04:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.40,0:04:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Onodera's running pretty late.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.82,0:04:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Whoa! Is that Onodera?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.95,0:04:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Crap. Is she looking for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.12,0:04:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Come to think of it, I never said that I'd wait inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.08,0:04:32.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What should I do? Should I call her?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.67,0:04:36.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh, did she spot me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.06,0:04:51.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.44,0:05:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,A-All right, then, should we get on with figuring out what we're getting for Chitoge-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.94,0:05:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I see. So she wants me to act like nothing happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.16,0:05:07.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Gotcha!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.16,0:05:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Man, Onodera's so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.66,0:05:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like coffee too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.75,0:05:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.96,0:05:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Doesn't matter how many times I see her, I'll never get over how cute she looks in her normal clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.21,0:05:19.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I bet she saw me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.25,0:05:21.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I wonder what we look like to others?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.88,0:05:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Do they think she's my girlfriend?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.68,0:05:28.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Girlfriend," huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.47,0:05:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Or are you planning to look for that boy you made that promise with ten years ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.56,0:05:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yeah right! As if I could just casually ask her about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.10,0:05:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.60,0:05:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think she'd really like for her birthday?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.40,0:05:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Well, lemme think...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.11,0:05:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Come to think of it, I don't know when Onodera's birthday is.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.91,0:05:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If it hasn't passed yet, maybe then I could give her something.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.49,0:05:54.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Ono—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.25,0:05:57.25,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! Let's go to all the shops and figure out what we'll get her!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.25,0:05:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure that'll be faster.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.92,0:06:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, were you saying something?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.63,0:06:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,No, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.00,0:06:06.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh, whatever. I'll have plenty of time to ask her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.76,0:06:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness we found something nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.47,0:06:17.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if Chitoge-chan will like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.69,0:06:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It was all over in the blink of an eye. I'm such a wuss!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.32,0:06:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Damn it! There were so many things I wanted to talk to her about!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.23,0:06:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But the whole time my heart felt like it was going to burst!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.79,0:06:38.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you have fun today, Ichijou-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.79,0:06:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.92,0:06:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.83,0:06:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Ruri-chan forced you to tag along with me today,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.05,0:06:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,so I was wondering if you were just humoring me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.51,0:06:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Don't be ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.30,0:06:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course I wasn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.89,0:06:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I had a good time, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.26,0:06:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. Thank goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.10,0:07:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, do you mind if we take a little detour?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.72,0:07:35.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Check out this view!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.85,0:07:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Who knew there was a place like this at the end of that narrow alley?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.98,0:07:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,No way would anyone find it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.31,0:07:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I found it by accident, years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.52,0:07:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It's my secret place.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.03,0:07:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Secret place, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.36,0:07:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh, crap, that makes me so happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.41,0:07:55.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But should she really be telling me about it, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.20,0:07:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it lovely?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.41,0:08:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, who else knows about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.42,0:08:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm guessing that Miyamoto, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.04,0:08:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,She doesn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.29,0:08:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I never told her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.34,0:08:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,This is our little secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.55,0:08:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't tell anyone about it, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.89,0:08:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What? You sure you want to share such an important secret with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.98,0:08:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course I'm sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.77,0:08:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I had a good time today too,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.23,0:08:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,so this is kind of my way of thanking you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.15,0:08:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}For real? Our little secret?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.24,0:08:38.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What am I gonna do? I'm so happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.16,0:08:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Come to think of it, hasn't Onodera been a little aggressive today?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.87,0:08:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}"Our little secret" has a great ring to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.87,0:08:46.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}All right! I should respond to Onodera's feelings, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.75,0:08:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Gotcha!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.67,0:08:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't tell a soul! I promise!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.93,0:09:01.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yup, it's a promise...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.10,0:09:03.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Raku-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.74,0:09:18.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, wow, calling you by your first name is so embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.45,0:09:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,It's so much easier to just call you Ichijou-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.20,0:09:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}For a moment there, I thought she was...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.83,0:09:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No, that was just me reacting to the word "promise."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.21,0:09:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If Onodera really were her...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.42,0:09:34.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's no way things could be that convenient.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.22,0:09:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Ichijou-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.72,0:09:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I really make you that uncomfortable by using your first name?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.01,0:09:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no, not at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.27,0:09:47.69,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, Onodera. Can I ask you something?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.35,0:09:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}C-Calm down now, Raku.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.56,0:09:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,There's something I've wanted to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.32,0:09:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.44,0:09:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Take advantage of the great mood right now,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.19,0:09:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and just ask her when her birthday is.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.49,0:10:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And then ask her if it's okay to take her out to celebrate.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.62,0:10:04.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But it might be too awkward if it were just the two of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.50,0:10:08.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Anyway, if I could celebrate Onodera's birthday with her...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.92,0:10:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,About the girl I made that promise with ten years ago... Was that you, Onodera?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.22,0:10:20.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wh-What did I just say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.76,0:10:23.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I was feeling so self-conscious that I just blurted it out!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.39,0:10:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}How am I gonna play this down now?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.81,0:10:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If I spring a question like that on her out of nowhere,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.73,0:10:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}there's no way she'd understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.06,0:10:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.95,0:10:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Onodera?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.21,0:10:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,At least... I think I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.42,0:10:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You mentioned it before, didn't you, Ichijou-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.38,0:11:00.47,Default,,0,0,0,,That there's someone you made a promise with ten years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.80,0:11:03.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I have someone like that too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.18,0:11:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Although my memory is fuzzy since it's from my childhood.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.81,0:11:11.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Ten years ago, the summer when I was five...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.90,0:11:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I became friends with a certain boy,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.73,0:11:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,and I received this key when we parted ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.36,0:11:21.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't remember his face or his name anymore,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.11,0:11:22.99,Default,,0,0,0,,but the one thing I do remember is...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.28,0:11:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems to me that...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.12,0:11:30.54,Default,,0,0,0,,he was wearing the same kind of locket that you wear.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.75,0:11:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The same locket?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.75,0:11:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Do coincidences like that exist?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.67,0:11:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Doesn't that mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.75,0:11:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}that Onodera was that girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.34,0:11:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. When you asked me before if I'd ever seen your locket,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.72,0:11:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I was so taken aback that I automatically denied it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.85,0:11:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It was only that one summer that I played with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.27,0:11:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,But back then I was very shy,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.52,0:11:57.57,Default,,0,0,0,,yet he took me outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.15,0:12:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Somehow, I felt I could trust him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.45,0:12:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that I think of it, he might have been my...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.78,0:12:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,first love, if you will.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.37,0:12:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I was so surprised when I first saw your locket.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.17,0:12:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought that, just maybe, you were the same person, Ichijou-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.34,0:12:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I see. So that's why Onodera said that back then.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.80,0:12:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Even if it was ten years ago, and you were just kids...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.43,0:12:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You never know! Maybe it's still important to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.40,0:12:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,No, no. I don't think that's quite right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.40,0:12:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.70,0:12:49.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I... was {\i1}hoping{\i0} that you would be that boy, Ichijou-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.67,0:12:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Onodera?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.50,0:13:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What are...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.34,0:13:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.89,0:13:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What are you doing, Ichijou Raku! Get over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.86,0:13:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, Onodera, let's pick this up again later.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.86,0:13:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, we'd better hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.41,0:13:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If... If Onodera is the girl I made that promise with...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.87,0:13:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's still no proof, however.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.00,0:13:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.96,0:13:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If there was a simple way to just confirm it...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.64,0:13:57.77,Default,,0,0,0,,So this is Chitoge-chan's house?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.27,0:14:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,It's enormous!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.61,0:14:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I know. What do Chitoge-chan's parents do for a living?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.99,0:14:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What am I gonna do? My present isn't all that great.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.41,0:14:12.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Mistress would never measure people by the price of their gifts.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.41,0:14:14.29,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up with that smug face?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.29,0:14:15.54,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.54,0:14:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,what are you doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.17,0:14:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, please! Seishirou-chan, don't be such a stranger!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.96,0:14:21.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.84,0:14:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Chitoge-chan! Happy birthday!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.72,0:14:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-Wh... Wh-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.18,0:14:32.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What are you all doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.31,0:14:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,As it is your birthday, I've taken the liberty of secretly inviting all your friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.61,0:14:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,C-Come here a second, darling!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.90,0:14:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.86,0:14:55.83,Default,,0,0,0,,What should I do? I haven't told anybody that my family is a bunch of gangsters!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.83,0:14:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? You still freak out over that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.50,0:15:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean, "over that"?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.17,0:15:04.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Because of "that", I never had any real friends, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.09,0:15:06.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course I'm freaking out!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.51,0:15:12.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you guys! Wouldn't you know, this girl's family is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.22,0:15:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Gangsters?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.39,0:15:18.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Kinda like the yakuza in Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.48,0:15:23.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it! Chitoge-chan, you're a total rich girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.61,0:15:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,That's amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.86,0:15:29.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Because that makes you the same as Ichijou-kun, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.74,0:15:33.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.24,0:15:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,See? No problem!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.62,0:15:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, this is where we'll be holding the party.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.89,0:15:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Happy birthday, Mistress!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.56,0:16:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,A very happy birthday to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.31,0:16:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, so you turned sixteen today, eh, Mistress?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.44,0:16:08.57,Default,,0,0,0,,This kind of surprise never gets old, does it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.57,0:16:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Are those your friends with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.78,0:16:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,This the first time you've ever brought friends home, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.32,0:16:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, young ladies, nice to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.12,0:16:20.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, uh, yes, it's so nice to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.08,0:16:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? You don't seem like your usual self today, Mistress.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.67,0:16:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Like you're oddly happy!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.25,0:16:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.71,0:16:35.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, well, I see that your friends have come to the party as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.09,0:16:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome, we are pleased to have you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.10,0:16:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes! Thank you for having us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.52,0:16:47.90,Default,,0,0,0,,My, my! Is that Master Raku from the Ichijou clan?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.40,0:16:50.61,Default,,0,0,0,,That certainly puts me on the spot.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.61,0:16:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,After all, I'm sure that you have the most splendid gift for Mistress.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.45,0:16:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm starting to have reservations about presenting her my own gift.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.45,0:17:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I swear he's becoming more obvious with each passing second.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.96,0:17:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you go, Chitoge-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.71,0:17:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,This is for you. It's a stationery set!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.96,0:17:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I got you a book.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.76,0:17:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not that great, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.05,0:17:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not true! I'm so happy! Really!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.76,0:17:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Mistress! Mistress!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.72,0:17:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Please take a look at our gift to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.18,0:17:27.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Ta-da! One thousand Japanese folk CDs and a year's supply of bananas!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.44,0:17:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,We heard you like them!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.02,0:17:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Chitoge-chan, you like Japanese folk songs?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.69,0:17:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.07,0:17:38.28,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, I'm next.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.28,0:17:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure that it will pale in comparison to yours, Young Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.66,0:17:45.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Please accept this, Mistress!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.17,0:17:51.04,Default,,0,0,0,,A super-luxury, custom-ordered, Maybach!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.04,0:17:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.30,0:17:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I don't have a license, so no thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.30,0:18:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, come on, you, too! Young Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.22,0:18:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,You better make a splash!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.56,0:18:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Go for it! Go for it! Go for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.75,0:18:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Damn it, could you make it any harder to hand someone a present?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.36,0:18:19.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you go. Happy birthday!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.50,0:18:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, little punk, is this what I think it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.13,0:18:34.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You wouldn't be saying that Mistress is a gorilla, would you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.38,0:18:37.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? No way! I was trying to be serious!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.55,0:18:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,When I saw it in the store, I thought it was perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.06,0:18:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks. I love it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.44,0:18:50.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You okay with something like that, Mistress?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.52,0:18:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, if Mistress is okay with it, we're okay with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.11,0:18:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Mistress! Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.86,0:19:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.66,0:19:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You can smile like that too?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.54,0:19:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What, so you were here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.55,0:19:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I'm taking a break.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.80,0:19:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? Me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.88,0:19:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, I have to say, your taste in presents really sucks.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.39,0:19:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I almost burst out laughing!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.10,0:19:29.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell? So you put on an act after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.14,0:19:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't like it, you can just toss it, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.98,0:19:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Moron!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.27,0:19:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,We're a couple, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.78,0:19:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,If I don't cherish it, then people will start to suspect us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.49,0:19:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'm going to cherish it. \NBecause I have no choice, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.91,0:19:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me you actually really like it deep down!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.62,0:19:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Not a chance, you moron!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.62,0:19:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.50,0:19:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You're going to cherish it, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.46,0:19:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Damn it, you had me fooled with how sweetly you said it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.17,0:20:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My heart even skipped a beat just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.51,0:20:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wait, why is my heart skipping a beat for her?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.97,0:20:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I just found out Onodera could possibly be my promise girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.93,0:20:11.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's not a stretch to say that I've met the girl I'm destined to be with!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.31,0:20:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Raku, got a sec?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.61,0:20:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,There's something that I've been wanting to ask you for the longest time.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.19,0:20:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Mind if I ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.20,0:20:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you being so formal now?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.70,0:20:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The girl that you said you met ten years ago... Are you still in love with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.67,0:20:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You're still going on about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.92,0:20:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you, that's not what she and I were like—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.84,0:20:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.00,0:20:40.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The girl from ten years ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.96,0:20:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I haven't necessarily confirmed anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.26,0:20:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but what I found out means that it has to be Onodera, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.68,0:20:48.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If that's the case...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.27,0:20:51.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.77,0:20:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You are?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.73,0:20:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, do the words,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.61,0:21:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,"Zawsze in love,"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.36,0:21:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,ring a bell?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.20,0:21:06.07,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
